难以确定的问题。与黑色星期五不同，在黑色星期五，您在大多数零售商处都可以省下一些钱，但对于这些广受欢迎的小工具来说，黄金日的销售情况更加难以预测。今年，Prime Day 优惠对大多数 AirPods、一些 MacBook 和少数 iPad 进行了折扣，其中还包括一些最新设备。以下是您可以获得的最佳 Apple Day 优惠。</p><h2> AirPods Pro（第二代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="ba359120b39d4bf9b1b9b5e3379f1bea" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAThTWLFJ1_6jDdor75Ndek1uPvqfNtiiMIjGKCtZIMvq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0BDHWDR12" class="rapid-with-clickid">第二代 AirPods Pro</a>在 Prime Day 期间售价 199 美元。这是 50 美元的折扣，也是我们见过的最优惠的价格。在<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">我们的耳塞指南</a>中，它们是 iPhone 用户的首选，与第一次迭代相比有了很大的改进，具有更好的降噪效果和整体改进的声音。它们具有出色的透明模式，让您在听音乐的同时仍能留意周围的声音，它们与 iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 完美搭配，并充分利用 Siri 的帮助。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html">我们</a><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html">在评测中给了他们 88 分</a>，指出音质既身临其境又细致，即使在较低音量下也能保持清晰。电池续航时间比苹果承诺的 6 小时多了 15 分钟，而且充电盒还能为耳机多充电 3 次。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Apple AirPods Pro（第二代）的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>AirPods（第 3 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="ebb499ea37c04874b033149e33cf6527" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple 更新版<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQuzFNN_zyKG0dueAZsGRNMrT_TyPXS7BXapegtBL-R2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Lightning-Resistant-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB0BDHB9Y8H%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">AirPods</a>在 Prime Day 折扣至 140 美元。这些<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airpods-review-2021-160026883.html">无线耳机</a>于 2021 年发布，几乎在各个方面都比前代产品有所改进。它们具有更好的音质、更舒适的设计和更长的电池寿命。 They don&#39;t have ANC like the AirPods Pro do, but it&#39;s hard to beat the third-gen AirPods at this price for iPhone users.</p><h2> AirPods (2nd gen) </h2><p><core-commerce id="d56e7dfba72143e38182150e17ab6075" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdQWEdRQzFRLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOTgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjU2ZDlmODlkLTVhZjktNDI3YS1iMTVmLTFlOTk3YzVhYjAwZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAS-uW2RRbmjjIWfn1pzgStQ4MKOx_ooeOnioEuygbEJF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07PXGQC1Q%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">second-generation AirPods</a> are down to $89 for Prime Day. These wireless earbuds are a bit old at this point, but if you have less than $100 to send and want a pair that work seamlessly with iPhones and other Apple devices, these are a good option. They fit similarly to Apple&#39;s EarPods and they have improved wireless range.</p><h2> AirPods Max </h2><p><core-commerce id="eef7103ae2494dd18f5fd4e1e8850037" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple&#39;s over-ear headphones, the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66e