palatable, but <a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-studio-display-review-mac-monitor-154504997.html">we still think</a> the display is ideal only for true Apple devotees. The A13 Bionic chip inside makes it a little smarter than most displays, but the 60Hz refresh rate is disappointing. Still, it&#39;s got a nice build with good speakers and a bright and accurate screen.</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。 Shop the</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>best Prime Day deals</em></a> <em>on Yahoo Life. Follow Engadget for the</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:51;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>best Amazon Prime Day tech deals</em></a> <em>.</em>在 In the Know 上<em>了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/tag/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day 趋势</em></a><em>。聆听 Autoblog 的汽车专家讲述与汽车相关的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:53;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/article/amazon-prime-day-2023/"><em>Prime Day 必买优惠</em></a><em>，并</em><em>在 AOL 上查找</em><a data-i13n="cpos:54;pos:1" href="https://www.aol.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-day-090057255.html"><em>Prime Day 促销信息</em></a>，这些都是专为您精心挑选的。</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-amazon-prime-day-apple-deals-on-airpods-macbooks-and-more-123422037.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-amazon-prime-day-apple-deals-on-airpods-macbooks-and-more-123422037.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 56d9f89d-5af9-427a-b15f-1e997c5ab00f</guid><dc:creator>艾米·斯科海姆</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 12:34:22 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689165264</ingest