 our favorite Chromebooks</a> , and while you can find more powerful models, this C423 laptop should work well if you plan on using the machine for web browsing, email checking and other simple tasks. If you&#39;d rather invest in a strong Chromebook, <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kZWFsLzI1NjViMjE3P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFhOS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMzVhOGFiZmYtZjlmMS00OGU4LTg0MjgtZmQzNDhiMDcwNTc5In0&amp;signature=AQAAAbKqW5B9aoRfqMrIWp9Gt_xfY14-Ca7N5MtxQBrPXG-d&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdeal%2F2565b217" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/deal/2565b217?showVariations=true&amp;pf_rd_r=CAF504CNTPMKRN14Q5TV&amp;pf_rd_t=Events&amp;pf_rd_i=primeday&amp;pf_rd_p=0f855fc7-6931-4ecb-8fd6-0f3434773050&amp;pf_rd_s=slot-6&amp;ref=dlx_prime_gd_dcl_img_17_2565b217_dt_sl6_50" class="rapid-with-clickid">this Prime Day sale</a> also includes the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9DaHJvbWVib29rLUNvbnZlcnRpYmxlLVBlbnRpdW0tQ29ybmluZy1DUDMxNC0xSC1QMVE1L2RwL0IwQlNMVjRNS0Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMWE5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIzNWE4YWJmZi1mOWYxLTQ4ZTgtODQyOC1mZDM0OGIwNzA1NzkifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdZ-RABzIVDm13AfM3lomUe0BjRgUwW5cMrpYScvXDMc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChrom