><![CDATA[<p> iPads may be the most sought after tablets, but there are plenty of others on the market that are worth considering and many are on sale for <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/">Amazon Prime Day</a> . If you&#39;ve been eyeing a new iPad, you&#39;re in luck as many of Apple&#39;s tablets have been discounted for the shopping event. If you prefer Android, or simply don&#39;t want to enter the Apple ecosystem, Fire tablets, Samsung slabs and others are also on sale right now. Here are the best iPad and tablet deals for Prime Day 2023.</p><h2> Apple iPad (9th gen) </h2><p><core-commerce id="a217428324574d4da9b0f30ea9176424" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple&#39;s <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlHOUZQSFk2P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAR4RanmH0u4y6mVZaDJZzkYomqpnAtu8p-cYM8jFx-3k&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G9FPHY6" class="rapid-with-clickid">10.2-inch iPad</a> is down to $250, which matches the tablet&#39;s all-time low. Apple normally sells this 64GB model for $329, though we&#39;ve frequently seen it retail around $275 for most of the past few months. The 9th-gen iPad is the top budget pick in our <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">iPad buying guide</a> , and we gave it a <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-9th-generation-review-143045685.html">review score of 86</a> in 2021. If you need more storage, the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlHOTFUTE5KP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAActU3VFjJSpfnstly-W3h4jUWlZBPHQ3Qqxq52jvmHsS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G91TLNJ" class="rapid-with-clickid">256GB model</a> is also on sale for $389.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> This iPad&#39;s design is dated next to newer models, as it still has a Lightning port, Home button, thick bezels and a non-laminated display. But it still gets you a huge array of apps, and its A13 Bionic chip remains fast enough for light work and casual media consumption. It&#39;s also the only current iPad to still carry a headphone jack.</p><h2>苹果iPad Air </h2><p><core-commerce id="b667a774c2564a5282c713e840de5c21" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWM0hOMUtDP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAQrRp1X1r3sGnv6Z10V1r94Iq4tjpAgd866GBST83p1h&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09V3HN1KC" data-demonetize-referr